    public abstract class Abstract_Cell<E extends Abstract_Cell<E,T>,T extends AbstractDiscrete_CellState<T,? extends java.lang.Enum<?>>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for modeling a single Cell with a CellState inside a SimulationGrid.

    Created by th174 on 1/29/2017.
